{"type":"message","id":"73ba002b","parentId":"e954231e","timestamp":"2026-03-01T08:34:04.160Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Polymarket 模拟交易扫描结果：\n\n发现多个交易机会，主要集中在特朗普驱逐移民相关市场：\n\n1. **市场名称**: Will Trump deport less than 250,000?\n   - **概率**: 0%\n   - **推荐交易方向**: NO\n   - **策略类型**: VALUE\n\n2. **市场名称**: Will Trump deport 250,000-500,000 people?\n   - **概率**: 100%\n   - **推荐交易方向**: YES\n   - **策略类型**: MOMENTUM\n\n3. **市场名称**: Will Trump deport 750,000 or more people in 2025?\n   - **概率**: 1%\n   - **推荐交易方向**: NO\n   - **策略类型**: VALUE\n\n其余市场均为特朗普驱逐不同数量级移民的预测，概率均为0%，推荐方向为NO，策略类型为VALUE。\n\n注意：以上仅为模拟交易分析，不构成真实投资建议。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":11713,"output":223,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11936,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772354034346}}
